Output examples/settings/set-caption-margin.gif
Set Width 800
Set Height 225
Set Padding 30

Set FontSize 18
Set TypingSpeed 0.1
Set Theme "Catppuccin Macchiato"

Set CaptionAlignment "bottom-right"
Set CaptionMarginVertical 10
Set CaptionMarginRight 10

CaptionOn

Type "Margins? Who wants a margin??"
Sleep 2s
